## ----------------------------------------------------------------------- ##
## Advantages
## ----------------------------------------------------------------------- ##

- Platform independent, no/few dependencies
- Modular
- Faster
- Parallel (very easy)
- Open source
- Use as R package
- Handling of GenABEL gwa data
- Survival (faster!)
- Probability estimations, multiclass!
- Split selection weights


